{"tid":983540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【親母虐殺B】台歲半女被「不求人」打死 17歲媽同3親友：看到小孩哭就打","createTime":"2019-01-16T04:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T01:28:08.000Z","uid":54337,"like":6,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"f76fb45ce212a585177ee4b3012c4ad5f470ed5e","tid":983540,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:55:38.000Z","msg":"【親母虐殺B】台歲半女被「不求人」打死 17歲媽同3親友：看到小孩哭就打<br />\n<br />\n【新增動新聞】台灣發生駭人聽聞的虐童致死案件！台南一名1歲零6個月大女童昨晚因呼吸微弱，被母親送到醫院後不治。醫護人員發現女童身上及四肢有多處嚴重瘀傷、懷疑涉及家暴隨即報警。女童的17歲母親坦承因女童哭鬧不肯喝奶，因而用抓背的「不求人」打她，還稱「看到小孩哭就打」；與這名母親同住一屋的3名親友，也因涉案被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n台南市警方表示，昨晚10時許，醫院通報發現有女童被虐死亡。警員到場發現，女童屍體雙手雙腳和背部有大面積瘀青，確認是受虐致死，也忍不住表示：「看了很痛心，傷心」。"},{"pid":"65388a881629597c69fd3041819c648a5d023961","tid":983540,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"女童的薛姓母親向警方表示，女童昨晚吃奶時哭鬧，頻頻摔奶瓶拒吃，薛女於是拿「不求人」教訓女兒，反而讓女兒哭得更大聲。至晚上9時許，一名李姓男子開的士，接薛女、女童及其表姊及表姊夫到KTV夜唱，當車輛經過民生綠園，薛女發現女兒呼吸微弱，嚇得要李男把車調頭到醫院，把女童送到醫院急救。警察隨後在其寓所內查扣藤條、塑膠管、不求人等被懷疑用作虐打女童的工具。<br />\n<br />\n虐童案消息深夜曝光後，許多網友都不睡覺，相約到警局聲討這名母親。約凌晨一時起，近百網友包圍警局，警方發動兩至三波驅離行動。過程中，女童生母李姓男友駕駛的計程車，遭激動的民眾打破車尾擋風玻璃。有人怒罵「才1歲你們到底怎麼下得了手」、「Ｘ的，社會上就是有這種敗類」、「小寶貝不痛了，保佑他們一定要受到懲罰！」<br />\n<br />\n薛女已承認曾打女童，但不知道會那麼嚴重。薛女又推諉女童「中邪」、不好帶，才會出手管教，否認虐待，警方已報請檢察官，今早驗屍，釐清死因。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，女童姓李，前年7月出生，父母去年9月離異，女童交由薛女撫養。薛女不想待在娘家，被母親看管，於是帶着女兒投靠住在北區成大城社區的表姊、表姊夫。三個大人、一個小孩就住在兩房一廳的公寓內，開的士維生的李姓男子是表姊夫的好朋友，常到他們寓所暫住，因而也常跟女童相處。由於四人曾動手管教女童，警方把他們列為涉嫌疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》"},{"pid":"7c18e9b2e3a1abbd50173b2debd67cd136fdbd21","tid":983540,"uid":30952,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的風景是人"},{"pid":"4032dce8acfe2100c6fc41d616c48cf593e7d4b4","tid":983540,"uid":54337,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547609624_bd61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547609624_bd61.jpg&h=cdaba09b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547607256_d66b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547607256_d66b.jpg&h=ec3944cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547606665_878d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547606665_878d.jpg&h=9a4d0fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547607256_90d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547607256_90d3.jpg&h=97253e07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77b84f28dd3a37b21d283e7486fb0ec13477ded5","tid":983540,"uid":45788,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:59:03.000Z","msg":"17歲媽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n風化大國真係名不虛傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n套都唔駛直接上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d671d009ad12e0a0ec16ec9fc73f6c88680bb50b","tid":983540,"uid":54337,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547608748_a3da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547608748_a3da.jpg&h=73e879a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547608748_e61a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547608748_e61a.jpg&h=1dddc556&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"214c07563a3e9d4bfb12417ce72826c58db9d442","tid":983540,"uid":52942,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"咁後生根本未ready做人老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要去ktv"},{"pid":"74d06a6e8a766778f9ce0390944e47c360ea4c79","tid":983540,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣最美的風景是人</blockquote><br />\n你打錯字。<br />\n<br />\n台灣最美的風景是淫"},{"pid":"7db77b072323f759c94e021b4ffd0baa008e25db","tid":983540,"uid":17646,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:01:11.000Z","msg":"虐童案消息深夜曝光後，許多網友都不睡覺，相約到警局聲討這名母親。約凌晨一時起，近百網友包圍警局"},{"pid":"2fb38721787dd345e68c701a2e78ee644db3f954","tid":983540,"uid":230777,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:06:13.000Z","msg":"睇到張相，嗰BB女真係畀佢虐待到無忽好肉，啲肉同傷口係裂開同腫脹晒，真係好心痛。"},{"pid":"5bb0a2a8145ebf87a6976676b3379f0c014153fc","tid":983540,"uid":54337,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"條女應該係發黑牛肺西"},{"pid":"10984a7a6bb6bf264113f6c7414c2a03e3e48068","tid":983540,"uid":188310,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:14:21.000Z","msg":"賤種臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca1a3580a3c0b654767f63d36964c7812daa6f9","tid":983540,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"打佢老母臭閪啦"},{"pid":"0fea6edf120f80e6010b453cade0a04f5af87aea","tid":983540,"uid":49918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:18:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea3e190c57246ba93eec16f7d17d5e06f64b7fa3","tid":983540,"uid":38216,"li